  "detailed_description": "As a player, you can customize your preferred colors for gameplay. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2742740/extras/fea46eb5746e95fc0baf09825a80773a.poster.avif?t=1704612074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2742740/extras/fea46eb5746e95fc0baf09825a80773a.webm?t=1704612074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2742740/extras/fea46eb5746e95fc0baf09825a80773a.mp4?t=1704612074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>For the falling blocks, you can continuously alter their horizontal positions according to your strategic plan, and switch the distribution of their two colors, in order to achieve the objective of eliminating blocks of the same color.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2742740/extras/b50f04fa6c5ce504176ca30feb83c01a.poster.avif?t=1704612074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2742740/extras/b50f04fa6c5ce504176ca30feb83c01a.webm?t=1704612074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2742740/extras/b50f04fa6c5ce504176ca30feb83c01a.mp4?t=1704612074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
